creator: YoSoftTech
descriptionHtml:
Business Catalog App is designed to promote businesses in almost all sectors.
It digitally supports Vocal for Local.
It is easy to access as a one-page application. Customers can easily get all the information at one place.
★ Create Catalog: User can create multiple Catalogs
★ Share with Customer: Seller can send Catalogs information
very easily.
★ Use can search area/ pin code wise Catalogs
★ Direct Contact between Sellers and Customers.
Users can Search and Create all types of Online Catalogs including Service Catalogs, Brochures, Product Catalogs, Menus, Card Catalogs, Business-to-Business Catalogs, Retail Catalogs, Manufacturer-supported Catalogs, General Catalogs, Consumer Catalogs.


How to Use Business Catalogs App
For Sellers: How to Create Business Catalogs:
⦁ Starts Your Business Online Easily
⦁ Creating products and service Catalogs
⦁ Add description and Images.
⦁ Sharing products Catalogs
⦁ Manage and update products
⦁ Marketing and promoting your business
⦁ Receive Customer orders
⦁ Safe and Secure Payment
⦁ Sales status and Reports

For Buyers: How to Search Business Catalogs:
⦁ Change Postal Code wherever you go and Search area/ pin code wise Catalogs.
Select Service or Products.
View Details and Images
⦁ Contact Catalogs Owner directly through this App
• Calls • WhatsApp • Buy Online • Products Videos and Image sharing •Share Catalogs •Free Trail •Visit Shops •Schedule Appointment •Promotions


Key Features:
✓ Create Unlimited Catalogs
✓ List unlimited Products
✓ Add Items, Menus and its variants
✓ Add and update Service and products
✓ You can add details like name, description and adding multiple images
✓ Add and update all details related to product with product images
✓ Easy to Search item by name, description or by company
✓ Quick, Easy and user-friendly app
✓ Can Share product and its details and images at one click
✓ Receive messages from customers
✓ Customers can search Catalogs area/ pin code wise


Services that can mostly use this app:
• Home-made food services
• Grocery Store/ Kirana shop
• Local restaurants/ Food shops
• Household services - Carpenter, Plumber, Electrician and more
• Goods Delivery
• Transport Services
• Saloon and Beauty parlour
• Garments, Clothing, Tailer and Boutiques
• Footwear and accessories
• Home and decor
• Home, Garden & Pets
• Furniture & Furnishing
• Health & Fitness


Key Benefits
⦁ Direct business contact between sellers and customers
⦁ Increase recognition builds customer loyalty
⦁ App makes the sales and business growth
⦁ Efficient tool for customer engagement
⦁ Promote your business and Improve visibility
descriptionShort: The Business Catalog App is designed to promote medium to small businesses.
